highlights.text: “Shape of You” by Ed Sheeran has been on Top Songs Global the longest, at 163 weeks straight.
“No Time To Die” by Billie Eilish is the highest new entry on Top Songs Global at #4.
Justin Bieber has the most spots on Top Songs Global. “Intentions (feat. Quavo)” is the highest at #5.
“Get Me (feat. Kehlani)” by Justin Bieber and Kehlani is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Global, up 92 spots at #72.
